{"tid":1702274,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"白粉報: 壓力煲炸彈 本小殺傷力大","createTime":"2019-11-09T15:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T11:36:46.000Z","uid":101345,"like":22,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"baf5a5b01f1ff9e2479c2669e31ee017f6eff3ee","tid":1702274,"uid":101345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:07:39.000Z","msg":"小資料：壓力煲炸彈 本小殺傷力大<br />\n <br />\n警方在是次爆炸現場附近，發現懷疑是由壓力煲製成的爆炸裝置，連接手提電話和電線。事件令人聯想起三年前的波士頓馬拉松恐襲案，當時的計時炸彈同樣由壓力煲製成，內藏大量鋼珠及鐵釘等，殺傷力強，但成本不到一百美元（約七百八十港元）。壓力煲炸彈為回教武裝組織及右翼激進分子常用的土製武器，策動九一一恐襲的阿蓋德亦曾在其網上雜誌，教授如何自製該種炸彈。<br />\n<br />\n白粉報唔貼url:<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20160919/mobile/odn-20160919-0919_00180_005.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20160919%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20160919-0919_00180_005.html&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpmipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=65666ba8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20160919/mobile/odn-20160919-0919_00180_005.html</a>"},{"pid":"9e3c8ac8519c364c5b9f583a60e12c2ee6a1571e","tid":1702274,"uid":101345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:08:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7aeeae14fd898233f582ce8d728f13dee94b4150","tid":1702274,"uid":101345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:09:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4ede1112edd50ca5bc880ff0094c5633fb30135","tid":1702274,"uid":101345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:12:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"88096596c5cff2a8450f9842a144ac13f8bcba9f","tid":1702274,"uid":130079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:13:17.000Z","msg":"拉<br />\n唔好推"},{"pid":"4cbaef76d6ea7ac51fec0809b9a39e09bc53b3d8","tid":1702274,"uid":11484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:15:14.000Z","msg":"大家千奇唔好亂咁學"},{"pid":"efcf065531114156f25d597b81d639b85720e277","tid":1702274,"uid":1